---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Week 12: 落下運動と放物運動">
  <h1>Week 12: 落下運動と放物運動</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">空を飛ぶ物体の秘密！</p>

  <h2>🎯 今日の目標</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>自由落下・鉛直投げ上げを計算できる</li>
    <li>水平投射を理解する</li>
    <li>斜方投射の計算ができる</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>鉛直方向の運動</h2>

  <h3>自由落下（初速度 0 で落下）</h3>
  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">v = gt</span>
    <span class="big-formula">y = ½gt²</span>
    <span class="big-formula">v² = 2gy</span>
  </div>

  <h3>鉛直投げ上げ</h3>
  <p>上向きを正とすると、加速度は <strong>−g</strong></p>

  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">v = v₀ − gt</span>
    <span class="big-formula">y = v₀t − ½gt²</span>
  </div>

  <h3>最高点</h3>
  <div class="highlight-box">
    最高点では <strong>v = 0</strong>！
  </div>

  <table>
    <tr><th>求めるもの</th><th>公式</th></tr>
    <tr><td>到達時間</td><td>t = v₀ / g</td></tr>
    <tr><td>最高点の高さ</td><td>h = v₀² / 2g</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>水平投射</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    水平方向に投げ出す運動 → <strong>横と縦を分けて考える！</strong>
  </div>

  <table>
    <tr><th>方向</th><th>運動の種類</th><th>公式</th></tr>
    <tr><td>水平（x）</td><td>等速度運動</td><td>x = v₀t</td></tr>
    <tr><td>鉛直（y）</td><td>自由落下</td><td>y = ½gt²</td></tr>
  </table>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>高さ h から水平に投げる</h4>
    <p>落下時間：t = √(2h/g)</p>
    <p>水平到達距離：x = v₀ × √(2h/g)</p>
  </div>

  <h2>斜方投射</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    角度 θ で投げる → 初速度を分解！
  </div>

  <h3>🎮 抛体大炮シミュレーター</h3>
  <div class="animation-container">
    <canvas id="cannonCanvas" width="500" height="300"></canvas>
    <div class="cannon-controls">
      <label>
        角度 θ: <span id="angle-val">45</span>°
        <input type="range" id="angle-slider" min="10" max="80" value="45" />
      </label>
      <label>
        初速度 v₀: <span id="velocity-val">30</span> m/s
        <input type="range" id="velocity-slider" min="10" max="50" value="30" />
      </label>
      <button id="fire-btn">🚀 発射！</button>
    </div>
    <div class="cannon-info">
      <span>飛距離: <strong id="range-val">--</strong> m</span>
      <span>最高点: <strong id="height-val">--</strong> m</span>
      <span>滞空時間: <strong id="time-val">--</strong> s</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">v₀x = v₀ cos θ</span>
    <span class="big-formula">v₀y = v₀ sin θ</span>
  </div>

  <table>
    <tr><th>方向</th><th>運動</th><th>公式</th></tr>
    <tr><td>水平</td><td>等速度</td><td>x = v₀ cos θ · t</td></tr>
    <tr><td>鉛直</td><td>投げ上げ</td><td>y = v₀ sin θ · t − ½gt²</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h3>重要な公式</h3>
  <table>
    <tr><th>求めるもの</th><th>公式</th></tr>
    <tr><td>最高点の高さ</td><td>h = (v₀ sin θ)² / 2g</td></tr>
    <tr><td>滞空時間</td><td>T = 2v₀ sin θ / g</td></tr>
    <tr><td>飛距離</td><td><strong>R = v₀² sin 2θ / g</strong></td></tr>
  </table>

  <div class="highlight-box warning">
    <strong>⚠️ 最大飛距離：θ = 45° のとき！</strong>
    <p>R_max = v₀² / g</p>
  </div>

  <h2>例題</h2>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題1：鉛直投げ上げ</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>初速度 20 m/s で投げ上げ。最高点の高さと到達時間は？（g = 10）</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>t = v₀/g = 20/10 = <strong>2 s</strong></p>
    <p>h = v₀²/2g = 400/20 = <strong>20 m</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題2：水平投射</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>高さ 45 m から水平に 10 m/s で投げる。落下時間と水平到達距離は？</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>t = √(2×45/10) = √9 = <strong>3 s</strong></p>
    <p>x = 10 × 3 = <strong>30 m</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題3：斜方投射の飛距離</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>初速度 20 m/s、角度 30° で投げる。飛距離は？（g = 10）</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>R = v₀² sin 2θ / g = 400 × sin 60° / 10</p>
    <p>= 400 × 0.87 / 10 ≈ <strong>34.6 m</strong></p>
  </div>

  <h2>練習問題</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>問題</th><th>解答</th></tr>
    <tr>
      <td>① 初速度 30 m/s で投げ上げ。最高点の高さは？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>h = 900/20 = 45 m</details></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>② 高さ 20 m から落下。地面に着くまでの時間は？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>t = √(40/10) = 2 s</details></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>③ 飛距離が最大になる角度は？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>45°</details></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h2>📝 今日のポイント</h2>
  <div class="highlight-box">
    <ul>
      <li>✓ 自由落下：v = gt, y = ½gt²</li>
      <li>✓ 投げ上げ：最高点で v = 0</li>
      <li>✓ 水平投射：横は等速、縦は自由落下</li>
      <li>✓ 斜方投射：<strong>v₀x = v₀cosθ, v₀y = v₀sinθ</strong></li>
      <li>✓ 最大飛距離：<strong>θ = 45°</strong></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week11/" class="nav-btn secondary">← Week 11</a>
    <a href="/physics-basic/" class="nav-btn">🏠 ホームへ</a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .subtitle { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: -0.5rem; }
  .formula-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe); border: 2px solid var(--primary); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .big-formula { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary-dark); display: block; margin: 0.5rem 0; }
  details summary { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; }
  
  #cannonCanvas {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #87CEEB 0%, #87CEEB 70%, #8B4513 70%, #8B4513 100%);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  .cannon-controls {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  .cannon-controls label {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .cannon-controls input[type="range"] {
    width: 120px;
  }
  #fire-btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    background: #ef4444;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.1s;
  }
  #fire-btn:hover { background: #dc2626; }
  #fire-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
  .cannon-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .cannon-info span {
    background: #f1f5f9;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
</style>

<script>
  const canvas = document.getElementById('cannonCanvas') as HTMLCanvasElement;
  const ctx = canvas?.getContext('2d');
  const angleSlider = document.getElementById('angle-slider') as HTMLInputElement;
  const velocitySlider = document.getElementById('velocity-slider') as HTMLInputElement;
  const angleVal = document.getElementById('angle-val');
  const velocityVal = document.getElementById('velocity-val');
  const fireBtn = document.getElementById('fire-btn');
  const rangeVal = document.getElementById('range-val');
  const heightVal = document.getElementById('height-val');
  const timeVal = document.getElementById('time-val');

  const g = 10;
  const scale = 3; // pixels per meter
  const groundY = 210;
  const cannonX = 40;
  const cannonY = groundY;
  
  let trajectory: {x: number, y: number}[] = [];
  let animating = false;
  let currentBall: {x: number, y: number, vx: number, vy: number, t: number} | null = null;

  function drawScene() {
    if (!ctx) return;
    ctx.clearRect(0, 0, 500, 300);
    
    // Sky gradient
    const skyGrad = ctx.createLinearGradient(0, 0, 0, groundY);
    skyGrad.addColorStop(0, '#87CEEB');
    skyGrad.addColorStop(1, '#B0E0E6');
    ctx.fillStyle = skyGrad;
    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, 500, groundY);
    
    // Ground
    ctx.fillStyle = '#8B4513';
    ctx.fillRect(0, groundY, 500, 90);
    ctx.fillStyle = '#228B22';
    ctx.fillRect(0, groundY, 500, 5);

    // Cannon base
    ctx.fillStyle = '#4a4a4a';
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.arc(cannonX, cannonY, 15, 0, Math.PI * 2);
    ctx.fill();
    
    // Cannon barrel
    const angle = parseInt(angleSlider?.value || '45') * Math.PI / 180;
    ctx.save();
    ctx.translate(cannonX, cannonY);
    ctx.rotate(-angle);
    ctx.fillStyle = '#2d2d2d';
    ctx.fillRect(0, -8, 40, 16);
    ctx.fillStyle = '#1a1a1a';
    ctx.fillRect(35, -10, 10, 20);
    ctx.restore();

    // Trajectory preview (dotted)
    if (!animating) {
      const v0 = parseInt(velocitySlider?.value || '30');
      const theta = parseInt(angleSlider?.value || '45') * Math.PI / 180;
      const vx = v0 * Math.cos(theta);
      const vy = v0 * Math.sin(theta);
      
      ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(100, 100, 100, 0.5)';
      ctx.setLineDash([5, 5]);
      ctx.beginPath();
      
      for (let t = 0; t < 10; t += 0.1) {
        const x = cannonX + vx * t * scale;
        const y = cannonY - (vy * t - 0.5 * g * t * t) * scale;
        if (y > groundY) break;
        if (t === 0) ctx.moveTo(x, y);
        else ctx.lineTo(x, y);
      }
      ctx.stroke();
      ctx.setLineDash([]);
    }

    // Drawn trajectory
    if (trajectory.length > 1) {
      ctx.strokeStyle = '#22c55e';
      ctx.lineWidth = 2;
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.moveTo(trajectory[0].x, trajectory[0].y);
      trajectory.forEach(p => ctx.lineTo(p.x, p.y));
      ctx.stroke();
      ctx.lineWidth = 1;
    }

    // Ball
    if (currentBall) {
      ctx.fillStyle = '#ef4444';
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.arc(currentBall.x, currentBall.y, 8, 0, Math.PI * 2);
      ctx.fill();
      
      // Velocity vectors
      const arrowScale = 0.5;
      // Horizontal (red)
      ctx.strokeStyle = '#dc2626';
      ctx.lineWidth = 3;
      drawArrow(ctx, currentBall.x, currentBall.y, currentBall.x + currentBall.vx * arrowScale, currentBall.y);
      // Vertical (blue)
      ctx.strokeStyle = '#2563eb';
      drawArrow(ctx, currentBall.x, currentBall.y, currentBall.x, currentBall.y - currentBall.vy * arrowScale);
      ctx.lineWidth = 1;
    }
  }

  function drawArrow(ctx: CanvasRenderingContext2D, x1: number, y1: number, x2: number, y2: number) {
    const headLen = 8;
    const angle = Math.atan2(y2 - y1, x2 - x1);
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(x1, y1);
    ctx.lineTo(x2, y2);
    ctx.lineTo(x2 - headLen * Math.cos(angle - Math.PI / 6), y2 - headLen * Math.sin(angle - Math.PI / 6));
    ctx.moveTo(x2, y2);
    ctx.lineTo(x2 - headLen * Math.cos(angle + Math.PI / 6), y2 - headLen * Math.sin(angle + Math.PI / 6));
    ctx.stroke();
  }

  function fire() {
    if (animating) return;
    
    const v0 = parseInt(velocitySlider?.value || '30');
    const theta = parseInt(angleSlider?.value || '45') * Math.PI / 180;
    const vx = v0 * Math.cos(theta);
    const vy = v0 * Math.sin(theta);
    
    trajectory = [];
    currentBall = { x: cannonX, y: cannonY, vx: vx * scale, vy: vy * scale, t: 0 };
    animating = true;
    
    // Calculate theoretical values
    const range = (v0 * v0 * Math.sin(2 * theta)) / g;
    const maxHeight = (v0 * v0 * Math.sin(theta) * Math.sin(theta)) / (2 * g);
    const totalTime = (2 * v0 * Math.sin(theta)) / g;
    
    if (rangeVal) rangeVal.textContent = range.toFixed(1);
    if (heightVal) heightVal.textContent = maxHeight.toFixed(1);
    if (timeVal) timeVal.textContent = totalTime.toFixed(2);

    animate();
  }

  function animate() {
    if (!currentBall || !animating) return;
    
    const dt = 0.05;
    currentBall.t += dt;
    
    const v0 = parseInt(velocitySlider?.value || '30');
    const theta = parseInt(angleSlider?.value || '45') * Math.PI / 180;
    const vx = v0 * Math.cos(theta);
    const vy = v0 * Math.sin(theta);
    
    currentBall.x = cannonX + vx * currentBall.t * scale;
    currentBall.y = cannonY - (vy * currentBall.t - 0.5 * g * currentBall.t * currentBall.t) * scale;
    currentBall.vy = (vy - g * currentBall.t) * scale;
    
    trajectory.push({ x: currentBall.x, y: currentBall.y });
    
    drawScene();
    
    if (currentBall.y >= groundY) {
      animating = false;
      currentBall.y = groundY;
      drawScene();
    } else {
      requestAnimationFrame(animate);
    }
  }

  angleSlider?.addEventListener('input', () => {
    if (angleVal) angleVal.textContent = angleSlider.value;
    trajectory = [];
    currentBall = null;
    drawScene();
  });

  velocitySlider?.addEventListener('input', () => {
    if (velocityVal) velocityVal.textContent = velocitySlider.value;
    trajectory = [];
    currentBall = null;
    drawScene();
  });

  fireBtn?.addEventListener('click', fire);

  drawScene();
</script>
